body_html: @girving Alright, could you then comment on which ops should be worked on? This is so that anyone who wants to contribute does not spend time on something that is not useful. For example, @ebrevdo mentioned that float64 for CTC ops may not be useful, and as you said the Sampler ops will also not be supported. Are there any other ops that need to be discarded from this list?

body: @girving Alright, could you then comment on which ops should be worked on? This is so that anyone who wants to contribute does not spend time on something that is not useful. For example, @ebrevdo mentioned that float64 for CTC ops may not be useful, and as you said the Sampler ops will also not be supported. Are there any other ops that need to be discarded from [this list](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/1140#issuecomment-227012645)?
